lead_paragraph: LEEDS--Dalia. A beauty her entire life. A woman of warmth, loving-kindness, loyalty, and devotion to family. Dalia was a friend for over six decades and our hearts go out to Larry and the family. Daniel and Joanna Rose 1/3
